<reg_short_dscr>:
AN break_link timer
------------------------------
<field_public_text>:
break_link_timer setting. 
Default value corresponds to 70ms for a System clock of 1.6ns and Timer Divider of 4.
------------------------------
<reg_short_dscr>:
AN aneg_wait timer
------------------------------
<field_public_text>:
an_wait_timer setting.
Default value corresponds to 38ms for system clock period of 1.6ns and timer divider of 4.
------------------------------
<reg_short_dscr>:
AN link_fail_inhibit timer
------------------------------
<field_public_text>:
10g link_fail_inhibit_timer setting. 
Default value is set to 50ms for a system clock period of 1.6ns and a timer divider value of 4. 
Long timer and short timer are set to same values as there is a training timer in TRAIN state which takes care of the training time of 500ms.
------------------------------
<reg_short_dscr>:
AN link_fail_inhibit_short timer
------------------------------
<field_public_text>:
1g link_fail_inhibit_timer setting
Default value is set to 50ms for a system clock period of 1.6ns and a timer divider value of 4.
------------------------------
<reg_short_dscr>:
